      <title>基于Hexo+coding建立的个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/03/ji-yu-hexo-coding-jian-li-de-ge-ren-bo-ke/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/03/ji-yu-hexo-coding-jian-li-de-ge-ren-bo-ke/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基于Hexo-coding建立的个人博客"><a href="#基于Hexo-coding建立的个人博客" class="headerlink" title="基于Hexo+coding建立的个人博客"></a>基于Hexo+coding建立的个人博客</h1><h2 id="一些废话"><a href="#一些废话" class="headerlink" title="一些废话"></a>一些废话</h2><p>原博客<code>sunminhuai.xyz</code>由于域名到期、腾讯<code>cloud studio</code>升级、操作失误等因素导致无法访问+博文丢失，还好保存了一份数据库文件以便日后逐步恢复旧博文</p><h2 id="博客建站技术"><a href="#博客建站技术" class="headerlink" title="博客建站技术"></a>博客建站技术</h2><p>博客建站技术非常多，本文仅将个人已知的方法归为博客平台、动态网页、静态网页3类。</p><h3 id="博客平台"><a href="#博客平台" class="headerlink" title="博客平台"></a>博客平台</h3><ul><li>CSDN，简书，wordpress等传统博客平台，大部分平台免费且有广告但访问量大适合推广，少部分平台收费但访问量很少</li><li>知乎、语雀、gitbook、baklib等新兴内容平台，免费且访问量不错</li></ul><h3 id="需要服务器的动态网页"><a href="#需要服务器的动态网页" class="headerlink" title="需要服务器的动态网页"></a>需要服务器的动态网页</h3><ul><li>最常见的就是一般的建站技术，即主机+建站程序，经过本人实践证实想要好的建站体验还是要花钱，也有少部分低价甚至免费主机但体验不好，免费的要么不稳定要么需要不断做推广续期，而国内服务器的备案还超级麻烦，建站程序有Wordpress，Typecho等<blockquote><p>收集到的一些免费主机</p><ul><li>AWS和谷歌云的免费使用一年服务，但需要支持VISA的信用卡，折腾起来挺麻烦的（AWS中国区不支持个人申请貌似需要企业执照，淘宝mastercard卡是1块）</li><li>三丰云，<a href="https://www.sanfengyun.com/free/#free_server" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费虚拟主机和云服务器</a></li><li>阿贝云，<a href="https://www.abeiyun.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费虚拟主机和云服务器</a></li><li>萝莉云，<a href="http://yunloli.com/index.php/buy/index/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">很便宜也有免费的</a></li><li>主机屋，<a href="http://www.zhujiwu.com/vhost/free.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费空间</a></li><li>主机蛋，<a href="http://www.idcegg.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费空间</a></li><li><a href="http://www.vpsxxs.com/category/mianfeivps/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">综合免费信息</a>，<a href="https://www.128sj.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费空间网</a></li><li>慧选，<a href="https://www.089.com.cn/category-1496.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">免费主机</a></li><li>硅云，<a href="https://www.vpsor.cn/activity/freevhost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1元主机</a></li><li><a href="https://rthe.cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">热铁盒</a></li><li><a href="http://www.hhhbhhb.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">沐云</a></li></ul></blockquote></li><li>另一种方法就是利用<code>cloud studio</code>的动态部署功能可以实现免费建站，旧站点<code>sunminhuai.xyz</code>就是使用该方法建立的wordpress站点，但站点会偶尔访问不了或者访问很慢，而目前<code>cloud studio</code>被腾讯升级后貌似已经没有动态部署功能了</li></ul><h3 id="不需要服务器的静态网页"><a href="#不需要服务器的静态网页" class="headerlink" title="不需要服务器的静态网页"></a>不需要服务器的静态网页</h3><ul><li>主要就是框架+托管的方式，框架有Hexo、Jekyll、Vuepress等等，托管平台有github、coding、码云（免费版不能自动部署，pages pro收费）等，该方法需要自己搭建环境，较为繁琐，但可拓展性很高，部分涉及写作的命令、代码已经可以使用插件代替，如hexoeditor、hexoblogclient等，尤其是hexo的插件、主题市场非常丰富，需要吐槽的是github的国内下载速度超慢</li><li>作为该方法的优化，出现了客户端+框架+托管的方式，如Gridea+coding的方式，该方法非常简单快速，但扩展性不足，需要吐槽的是其自带的编辑器bug不少；还有就是本博客使用的hexoeditor+hexo+coding的方式，可以实现一键部署等功能</li></ul><h2 id="搭建博客"><a href="#搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="搭建博客"></a>搭建博客</h2><p>需求：尽可能免费或者低价，稳定简便，本地存储，书写优雅<br>方案：采用hexoeditor编写并本地存储+一键部署+Coding托管的方式<br>安装步骤：</p><ul><li>安装git，安装nodejs</li><li>git bash here</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token keyword">set</span> registry<span class="token operator">=</span>http://registry.npm.taobao.org/<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#根据个人需要设置淘宝镜像加速下载，本人更换后下载并没有变快</span><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token keyword">set</span> registry https://registry.npmjs.org<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#恢复原镜像</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> -g hexo-cli<span class="token function">npm</span> init<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#安装hexo</span>hexo ghexo s<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#产生静态文件并运行服务器，打开http://localhost:4000能看到博客就说明安装成功</span><span class="token function">git</span> clone https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery.git<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#下载hexo-theme-matery主题</span></code></pre><ul><li>安装<a href="https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-theme-matery</a>主题：在<code>_config.yml</code>中更改<code>theme:landscape</code>为<code>theme:hexo-theme-matery</code></li><li>在coding免费团队版中建立项目，初始化，开启page服务，具体参考<a href="http://dugblog.coding.me/Hexo/20180616-build-blog-hexo-next-windows.html#HexoEditor" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a></li><li>在<code>_config.yml</code>中找到<code>deploy</code>，更改配置</li></ul><pre class=" language-yml"><code class="language-yml">deploy:  type: git # 必须填git  repo: # coding仓库的http地址  # repo示例 https://e.coding.net/用户名/项目名/仓库名.git  branch: master # 分支  message: blog update # 每次更新时提交的备注</code></pre><ul><li>测试部署博客</li></ul><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save hexo-deployer-githexo cleanhexo g -d <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#若coding仓库中代码更新并可以正常访问page，则部署成功，输入d后会要求填用户名和密码，需要注意coding团队版是邮箱和密码登录而非用户名</span></code></pre><ul><li>在<code>_config.yml</code>中更改博客设置，更多设置参考<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a></li></ul><pre class=" language-yaml"><code class="language-yaml"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Site</span><span class="token key atrule">title</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> Hexo         <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为你站点的标题</span><span class="token key atrule">subtitle</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>           <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为你站点的副标题</span><span class="token key atrule">description</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为你站点的说明</span><span class="token key atrule">keywords</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>           <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为你站点的关键字</span><span class="token key atrule">author</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> John Doe    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为你的名字</span><span class="token key atrule">language</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>           <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为 zh-CN</span><span class="token key atrule">timezone</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>           <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此处改为 Asia/Shanghai</span></code></pre><ul><li>主题安装后需要在<code>\hexo\source\</code>下分别建立<code>\about</code>、<code>\categories</code>、<code>\tags</code>等文件夹，并分别在里面建立<code>\index.md</code>文件</li></ul><pre class=" language-text"><code class="language-text">---title: "about"type: aboutlayout: "about"---# 其它分别以categories、tags等替换about，若还有其他页面找不到就按相同方法建立index即可</code></pre><ul><li>在主题的<code>_config.yml</code>中更改主题设置，具体参考<a href="https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery/blob/develop/README_CN.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">主题文档</a><ul><li>更改图片替换文件夹文件即可</li><li>更改图标在<code>E:\博客\hexo\themes\hexo-theme-matery\source\libs\awesome\css\all.css</code>和<a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons" target="_blank" rel="noopener">图标网站</a>中查询</li><li>评论系统：使用<a href="https://valine.js.org/quickstart.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">valine</a>，不需要登陆，主题内置，配置简单</li><li>更改梦想栏为<a href="https://hitokoto.cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一言</a>，参考<a href="https://chen-shang.github.io/2019/08/15/ji-zhu-zong-jie/hexo/hexo-theme-matery-zhu-ti-you-hua/#toc-heading-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">博文</a>，保留引用来源参考<a href="https://yafine-blog.cn/posts/153b.html?tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a></li></ul></li></ul><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>script src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bluebird@3/js/browser/bluebird.min.js"</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>script<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>script src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/whatwg-fetch@2.0.3/fetch.min.js"</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>script<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token operator">--</span>End<span class="token operator">--</span><span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>script<span class="token operator">></span>     <span class="token function">fetch</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'https://v1.hitokoto.cn'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>         <span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">then</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>res<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>             <span class="token keyword">return</span> res<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">json</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>         <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>         <span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">then</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>data<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>             <span class="token keyword">var</span> hitokoto <span class="token operator">=</span> document<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getElementById</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'hitokoto'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>             hitokoto<span class="token punctuation">.</span>innerText <span class="token operator">=</span> data<span class="token punctuation">.</span>hitokoto <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">' \n '</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">' \n '</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">'——『'</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">' '</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> data<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token keyword">from</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">' '</span> <span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token string">'』'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>         <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>         <span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token keyword">catch</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>err<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>             console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">error</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>err<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>         <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>script<span class="token operator">></span></code></pre><ul><li>添加关于小站：思路就是通过ejs模板建立新页面；先在主题配置文件中的<code>about</code>下添加二级菜单<code>关于小站</code>，指向<code>/about</code>，图标用<code>fab fa-internet-explorer</code>；然后打开<code>theme/matery/layout/about.ejs</code>文件，大约在13行有一个<code>&lt;div class="card"&gt;</code>标签，在之前新增如下代码，之后在<code>/source/about/index.md</code>下面写上内容即可</li></ul><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div <span class="token keyword">class</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"card"</span><span class="token operator">></span>    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div <span class="token keyword">class</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"card-content"</span><span class="token operator">></span>        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div <span class="token keyword">class</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"card-content article-card-content"</span><span class="token operator">></span>            <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div <span class="token keyword">class</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"title center-align"</span> data<span class="token operator">-</span>aos<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"zoom-in-up"</span><span class="token operator">></span>                <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>i <span class="token keyword">class</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"fab fa-internet-explorer"</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>i<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>nbsp<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>nbsp<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">%</span><span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token function">__</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'关于小站'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">%</span><span class="token operator">></span>            <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>                <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"articleContent"</span> data<span class="token operator">-</span>aos<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"fade-up"</span><span class="token operator">></span>                    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">%</span><span class="token operator">-</span> page<span class="token punctuation">.</span>content <span class="token operator">%</span><span class="token operator">></span>                <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span></code></pre><ul><li>添加个人简历：先在主题配置文件中的<code>about</code>下添加二级菜单<code>个人简历</code>，指向<code>/resume</code>，图标用<code>fas fa-portrait</code>以修改工具栏图标，并新建<code>/hexo/source/resume/index.md</code>，<code>foront-matter</code>全部改为<code>resume</code>；然后新建<code>theme/matery/layout/resume.ejs</code>文件，新增以上同样的代码并改为<code>个人简历</code>，并更改对应的图标名以修改网页内图标，之后在<code>/source/resume/index.md</code>下面写上内容即可</li><li>更改友链为常用工具：跟以上类似，在主题配置文件中将工具栏图标改为<code>fas fa-toolbox</code>，在<code>\hexo\themes\hexo-theme-matery\layout\friends.ejs</code>中修改网页图标，在<code>\hexo\source\_data\friends.json</code>中修改需要的工具链接</li><li>添加html自定义页面<br>首先在站点目录下的source文件夹下新建<code>aboutme</code>文件，文件名可自定义，然后编写一个<code>index.html</code>放入<code>aboutme</code>文件夹下，然后在主题配置文件下的导航配置信息添加下面的配置：</li></ul><pre class=" language-yaml"><code class="language-yaml"><span class="token key atrule">About</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token key atrule">url</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> /    <span class="token key atrule">icon</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> fas fa<span class="token punctuation">-</span>address<span class="token punctuation">-</span>card    <span class="token key atrule">children</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>      <span class="token punctuation">-</span> <span class="token key atrule">name</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> 关于我        <span class="token key atrule">url</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> /about        <span class="token key atrule">icon</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> fas fa<span class="token punctuation">-</span>user<span class="token punctuation">-</span>circle      <span class="token punctuation">-</span> <span class="token key atrule">name</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> Another    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#这是新添加的，在原有配置基础上添加</span>        <span class="token key atrule">url</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> /aboutme        <span class="token key atrule">icon</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> fa fa<span class="token punctuation">-</span>user<span class="token punctuation">-</span>secret</code></pre><p>  然后在站点配置文件下，找到<code>skip_render</code>，在后面添加属性，如下：</p><pre class=" language-yaml"><code class="language-yaml"><span class="token key atrule">skip_render</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> aboutme/**  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 其意思为在对文件进行渲染时跳过aboutme文件下的所有文件</span></code></pre><ul><li>一键部署：测试了hexoeditor，hexoclient，hexoblogclent三款插件，仅hexoeditor可以正常使</li></ul><h2 id="其他资料"><a href="#其他资料" class="headerlink" title="其他资料"></a>其他资料</h2><ul><li>SEO优化：<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/92508540" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考1</a>，<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/80140893" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考2</a></li><li>免费图床：<blockqu